    "bio": "AI Systems Architect with 18+ years experience designing scalable, intelligent automation solutions. I specialize in architecting complex n8n workflows that integrate AI systems, streamline operations, and optimize business processes. My expertise spans multi-agent architectures, data automation, and enterprise-grade systems that adapt to evolving business needs. I help organizations unlock their potential through strategic technology implementation and innovative automation solutions.",
